  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Generic Name:</strong> Bremelanotide &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Brand Name:</strong> Vyleesi &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Type:</strong> Synthetic cyclic heptapeptide &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Molecular Formula:</strong> C<sub>50</sub>H<sub>68</sub>N<sub>14</sub>O<sub>10</sub> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Molecular Weight:</strong> 1,025.2 Da &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Origin:</strong> Derived from alpha-MSH / <a href="/articles/melanotan-2-guide">Melanotan II</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Route:</strong> Subcutaneous injection (autoinjector) &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>FDA Approval:</strong> June 2019 (HSDD in premenopausal women)</p>
