<p>Unlike its parent compound <a href="/articles/melanotan-2-guide">Melanotan II</a>, PT-141 was specifically engineered to isolate the pro-sexual effects while reducing melanogenic (skin-darkening) activity. It targets the brain's arousal circuitry rather than acting on peripheral blood vessels.</p>

<p>For a deeper compound profile, visit <a href="https://peptidearc.com">PeptideArc</a>.</p>

